        <h3 class="card-title">Key Price Levels to Watch</h3>
        <p>Bitcoin respects psychological round numbers and previous all-time highs. These levels act as magnets:</p>

        <ul class="levels-list">
          {keyLevels.map((level) => (
            <li><strong>{level.level}:</strong> {level.type}</li>
          ))}
        </ul>

        <p><strong>Pro Strategy:</strong> Set alerts at these levels. Major breakouts or bounces from these zones create the best trading opportunities.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="content-card">
        <h3 class="card-title">The Bitcoin Halving Cycle</h3>
        <p>Every ~4 years, Bitcoin's block reward is cut in half (the "halving"). This predictable supply shock has historically triggered massive bull runs:</p>

        <ul class="content-list">
          <li><strong>2012 Halving:</strong> BTC went from $12 to $1,100 (+9,000%)</li>
          <li><strong>2016 Halving:</strong> BTC went from $650 to $20,000 (+3,000%)</li>
          <li><strong>2020 Halving:</strong> BTC went from $8,500 to $69,000 (+700%)</li>
          <li><strong>2024 Halving:</strong> Bull run likely through 2025-2026</li>
        </ul>

