        <p><strong>2. 200-Week Moving Average</strong><br>
        Bitcoin has never closed below the 200-week MA for long. It's the ultimate "buy the dip" indicator for long-term investors.</p>

        <p><strong>3. Stock-to-Flow Model</strong><br>
        While not perfect, this model based on Bitcoin's scarcity has predicted major price trends. Use it for big-picture context.</p>
      </div>
